      <h4 style="margin-left: 10%; padding: 10px; width: 30%; color: black;
      background-color: tomato;">
        The proof is in the progress.
      </h4>

      <h5 style="margin-left: 17%; padding-top: 20px;">
        > Achieve your big goals
      </h5>
      <h5 style="margin-left: 17%; padding: 0;">
        > Break goals down into smaller steps.
      </h5>
      <h5 style="margin-left: 17%; padding: 0;">
        > Complete steps with proofs. 
      </h5>
      <h5 style="margin-left: 17%; padding: 0;">
        > Be self-accountable.

      </h5>
